tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE nft_metadata (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255),
    description TEXT,
    creator_name VARCHAR(100),
    creator_email VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE nft_ownership (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    nft_id UUID REFERENCES nft_metadata(id),
    owner_name VARCHAR(100),
    owner_address VARCHAR(255),
    purchase_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE nft_stats (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    nft_id UUID REFERENCES nft_metadata(id),
    views_count INT,
    likes_count INT,
    comments_count INT
);
